	* beast-gtk/bstracktable.[hc]: GtkTablke derived widget, that
	allowes for limited grid-aligned GUI editing.
	
	* beast-gtk/bstrtest.c: test program for bstracktable.
	
	* beast-gtk/bstapp.[hc]: fix main loop exit.
	
