	* beast-gtk/bstmaster.c: wrapped up MASTER debugging stuff.

	* beast-gtk/bstmain.c (bst_parse_args): new function to parse
	--beast-debug, --beast-no-debug args and evaluate BEAST_DEBUG and
	BEAST_NO_DEBUG env vars.

